Exim4u's Webmail is a modified version of Horde Groupware that is customized
and branded for inclusion with the Exim4U software suite.  Webmail should be
installed using the Horde PEAR channel as described in the WEBMAIL document
in the Exim4U root directory. Scripts are provided which will automatically
configure the Exim4U preferences, appearance features and file
ownerships/permissions.
